{"tid":1350193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有請文宣同伴] 請停止所有未經証實既黑吃黑POST!! 全力推番琴晚上環一事!!","createTime":"2019-07-22T12:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T17:47:09.000Z","uid":96371,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"dbb6f39f084f82b5e5e2533e4b22d05d8948c887","tid":1350193,"uid":96371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日熱門都係元朗, 出街番工都係元朗<br />\n上環催淚彈 亂開三鳩幾十槍既POST同討論真係兩隻手都數得晒<br />\n中上環一眾同伴俾人當CONDOM仔咁你地真係忍心咩!!!!<br />\n衰仔D現實D仆街D講一句, 寒左呢班最勇武肯為我地既家獻出所有既義士既心, 以後仲有咩人會出黎幫我地頂 為我地一齊爭取啊!!!<br />\n明白琴晚元朗一事係會令大家好憤怒想入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />左佢地D村起晒佢地老母D咸魚出黎煲湯!<br />\n但係!!! 個D乜撚野黑吃黑, 12點天水圍斬人 3點元朗開大片 6點沙田佢話事, 仲有乜撚野肥媽受訪嗚嗚嗚既POST, 推上黎把撚咩!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下大家快D停一停, 諗一諗我地而家最應該關注既係咩!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左光復元朗行動同一兩個發洩POST之前, 應該全力搜集番晒所有相同片出黎, 造文宣!!!<br />\n唔可以俾呢單野無聲消失左!! 更加唔可以對D狗閪開槍習以為常架!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72897db7075d182be8a49cd7e9b8e00dece5083e","tid":1350193,"uid":96371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:14:16.000Z","msg":"唔該丫"},{"pid":"801b04c5d68917e07a5c9304bd1075feaa5ff7f1","tid":1350193,"uid":96371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:14:27.000Z","msg":"求你地丫"},{"pid":"6766cf575baa66b4a3343fa2db4518331627fb7b","tid":1350193,"uid":96371,"like":1,"disli